divs: sighting detailsme and my friend were going to a bar after dinner. we were driving down rout 537. it was about 830. i am remembering this from around 1989. we saw the onject through the driver side window. it was a long distance from us. it traveled with us for about 25 min. it made no noise. it then turned and disapered. i watched it throuh the back window the car was a camaro with a big back window. we didn't say anything about it for a while that night. my freind saw it too. i don't know what made me spot it. it was a clear night. might have been the light \brighness of the object.it grabbed my attention from nowhere. i have driven that road often without seeing anything. i was intrigued, curious, scared and awed. i thought it was a plane or the moon at first.
Summary: It was oval /oblong strange shpe yellow white ike colro, not the moon. I think it may have had some Orange in it too.
